&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-style: italic;"&gt;King Charles III’s visit to the United States comes at a very peculiar time. Both his brother and his host have been embroiled in the Epstein scandal, and on top of that, Trump has strained relations with the United Kingdom because the British have expressed reservations about the war in Iran. I don’t think anyone would want to be in the king’s shoes right now… except, of course, his host.&lt;/p&gt;
